results.name: 2^(n-1) mod composite(n).
program: (PARI) lista(nn) = {compo = select(n->(! isprime(n) && (n != 1)), vector(nn, i, i)); for (i = 1, #compo, print1(2^(i-1) % compo[i], ", "););} \\ _Michel Marcus_, Sep 11 2013
